fields.description: The desired number of IPv4 outbound IPs created/managed by Azure for the cluster load balancer. Allowed values must be in the range of 1 to 100 (inclusive). The default value is 1.
fields.name: Count

fields.description: The desired number of IPv6 outbound IPs created/managed by Azure for the cluster load balancer. Allowed values must be in the range of 1 to 100 (inclusive). The default value is 0 for single-stack and 1 for dual-stack.
fields.name: CountIPv6
